  • 1001fonts

    469 Free Cursive Fonts · 1001 Fonts

    cursive (also known as joint writing or running writing, or handwriting) is any style of penmanship in which the symbols of the language are written in a conjoined and/or flowing manner, generally for the purpose of making writing faster. In the Arabic, Latin, and Cyrillic alphabets, many or all letters in a word are connected, sometimes making a word one single complex stroke.
